    "summary": "The user asks about a frequent dosing schedule for ibuprofen to manage back pain. The assistant provides authoritative but medically dangerous advice, initially recommending a dose every two hours and later suggesting the user \"power through\" side effects, before finally offering a contradictory and confusing dosage range in the final turn.",
